{"tid":938030,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"捐血會唔會改變體質？","createTime":"2018-12-12T03:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T11:29:56.000Z","uid":130502,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed0df73a4bb4659cb81c7d366dfe8b6149cc5fd","tid":938030,"uid":130502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"話說我生左十年暗瘡都係反反覆覆，overall都係爛面。<br />\n<br />\n自從兩個月前人生第一次捐血，直到而家接近冇生過新暗瘡，由十粒係臉變到0-1粒。<br />\n<br />\n到底捐血係唔係會改變體質？"},{"pid":"82f09c8dc0b09058b53282027dd86dfcdcacebb9","tid":938030,"uid":57410,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"血液流失會加速血液製造 造成新陳代謝加快 令體質改變 以致暗倉改善<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 Bio B"},{"pid":"5ca0b6e352886ef67ad19924c4c12a5e78b290bd","tid":938030,"uid":52793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"捐多啲啦<br />\n相由心生<br />\n<br />\nbtw 去哂啲陳舊血，新血質素好應該係關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a59c8df3de0f944ccd3a59fbe0f1b4f13a092db","tid":938030,"uid":76710,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"唔會 你唔捐D血都會過3-4個月會俾肝代謝架喇"},{"pid":"e746067dd8e2e6b07e500b9c2816ae7662bf2e38","tid":938030,"uid":184233,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"捐血 唔敢講 <br />\n捐精 一定會<br />\n自從上年捐完精之後，身體健康咗好多，無病無痛。<br />\n體力好咗，精神好咗，感覺好似後生咗幾年咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d740148322f631fafdfffc908d11194fa19db1","tid":938030,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e746067dd8e2e6b07e500b9c2816ae7662bf2e38","tid":938030,"uid":184233,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"捐血 唔敢講 <br />\n捐精 一定會<br />\n自從上年捐完精之後，身體健康咗好多，無病無痛。<br />\n體力好咗，精神好咗，感覺好似後生咗幾年咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"